          "Use torch.fx.symbolic_trace(model) to obtain the FX graph",
          "Apply torch.nn.utils.fuse_conv_bn_eval(conv_module, bn_module) on each Conv2d+BatchNorm2d pair",
          "Alternatively, use torch.quantization.fuse_modules(model, [['conv', 'bn', 'relu6']]) for MobileNet-style blocks",
          "Verify output equivalence: torch.testing.assert_close(original(x), fused(x), atol=1e-4, rtol=1e-4)",
          "Re-run torch.compile(fused_model, mode='max-autotune') to allow Inductor to re-fuse across new op boundaries"
